<Link id="l02884" /><CodeLine lineNumber="2884"><Highlight kind="comment">/// This is the underlying implementation of all of the</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l02885" /><CodeLine lineNumber="2885"><Highlight kind="comment">/// ConstantDataSequential::get methods.  They all thunk down to here, providing</Highlight></CodeLine>
